{"tid":2209863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚文豪轟明日大嶼︰冇飯開仲裝修","createTime":"2020-09-20T03:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T03:10:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fef9a75b2b0ba87e554e5c1e567bdab4baef2486","tid":2209863,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/JFENWBBLRNAGRHPIIKY5CK2RUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FJFENWBBLRNAGRHPIIKY5CK2RUE%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=71fc11bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FJFENWBBLRNAGRHPIIKY5CK2RUE%2F&h=9bd78435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/JFENWBBLRNAGRHPIIKY5CK2RUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪轟明日大嶼︰冇飯開仲裝修<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/93rsOTQEr230XkDqlnWQMoQi104=/1963x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HWYN6CA7HRF5BNCUWSIGVWS72A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F93rsOTQEr230XkDqlnWQMoQi104%3D%2F1963x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHWYN6CA7HRF5BNCUWSIGVWS72A.jpg&h=a7ca84c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚文豪昨表明反對「明日大嶼」前期研究撥款。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉5.5億元的「明日大嶼」前期研究撥款，預料政府將於立法會延任一年期間，重新提交財委會審議。公民黨立法會議員譚文豪昨預計，6,000億元的明日大嶼工程在原材料加價等因素下，勢必超支，他擔心政府一旦獲撥款研究，日後就會以「洗濕了頭」為由，繼續要求立法會撥款。他又指，香港已出現移民潮，未來的土地需求成疑，故他反對「明日大嶼」及前期研究撥款。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪指，「明日大嶼」單是填海和興建連接人工島和陸地的四條鐵路，。。。。。。。。。。他質疑項目未來會嚴重超支，即使有前期研究都不會解決有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指移民潮下無需求<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪又表示，政府現時正出現財政問題，連第三輪防疫抗疫基金都要「縮水」，。。。。。。。。。。中國人口不再希望來港，質疑未來沒有龐大的土地需求。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨黨魁鍾國斌指未來政府收入很可能會減少，。。。。。。。。。。。。了解工程的投資與回報與是合比例，屆時再決定是否進行計劃。"},{"pid":"51a4a885fb964c6168ea0737731d4bdfb1897a22","tid":2209863,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"不過做屋企裝修都繼續好旺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}